quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  52,15,"E ko mbilewu woni ﾉ容e lepte ﾉ容 sutiﾉ熔n? Kaa hara on alaa e yi'ude?"
  52,16,"Meeﾉ容e nguleeki ngee Yiite sumon nge ! Muﾃｱﾃｱiﾉ熔n ﾉ蓉m maa hara on muﾃｱﾃｱaaki, fow no fota e mon. On yoﾉ兎taake hannde, si wanaa ko geddi e keeferaaku ko gollaynoﾉ熔n kon aduna."
  52,17,"Pellet, hulirﾉ兎 Joomi mun ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔ftagol yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko woﾉ遼擁too e haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n, hino e Aljannaaji e naamaaji mawﾉ擁, ﾉ擁 taﾆｴondirtaa."
  52,18,"Ko ﾉ兎 dakmitorayﾉ兎 dakammeeji ﾃｱaametee e njaram e desal ko Allah okki ﾉ兎, Joomi maﾉ橡兎 daﾉ溶da ﾉ兎 lepte Jahiimi ﾉ容n. ﾆ‘ maliree daﾃｱugol dakamme yela maﾉ橡兎 on, e daﾉ溶deede lepte."
  52,19,"ﾆ‘ wi'anee ontuma : ﾃｱaamee yaron kala ko yiﾉ蓉ﾉ熔n, ko hannduﾉ兎 e mun, wata on hulu lorra ko ﾃｱaamoton maa ko yaroton kon. ﾆ隔m ko njoﾉ電i mon, e golle mon laaﾉ砥ﾉ容 ﾉ容n aduna."
  52,20,"Hara ko on soﾉ橡妬ndiiﾉ兎 e hoore danﾉ容 cuﾉ擁naaﾉ容 weertindiraa. Men resini ﾉ兎 kadi rewﾉ兎 yooﾉ預 giteeﾉ兎."
  52,21,"ﾆ‘n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎, genyngol maﾉ橡兎 ngol kadi jokki ﾉ兎 e gomﾉ擁nal ngal, Men tawtindinay ﾉ兎 e geyngol maﾉ橡兎 ngol, fii no ﾉ兎rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ砥uﾉ妬ra e fee maﾉ橡兎, hay si ﾉ兎n golliraano wano maﾉ橡兎. E hoore Men ﾉ蓉ytanoytaaﾉ兎 huunde e baraaji golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n; tawde neﾉ遼熔 kala ko tiginnde e bonﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 o faggitii ﾉ擁n, gooto ronnditantaako mo ko golli kon."
  52,22,"Men ﾉ兎ydanii ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎 Aljanna, nooneeje e muuyanteeﾉ擁 e kala ko ﾉ兎 tuuyetee e teewu."
  52,23,"Hiﾉ兎 jaaondira ka nder Aljanna ton : ﾃｱedduﾉ容 ﾉ容 jillaa njaram wa'uﾉ預m wa njaramji goo aduna; woni ko siwrinta adda cona-cana maa ko sabimbinta bakkaatu."
  52,24,"Hara sukaaﾉ兎 no eltanaaﾉ兎 hino wanngoo e maﾉ橡兎, wa'uﾉ兎 wa kaﾅ暁菊 reenaaﾉ容, hakkee ko ﾉ兎 jalbi."
  52,25,"Woﾉ遼兎 e yimﾉ兎 Aljanna ﾉ兎n fewtita ﾉ兎ya, ﾉ兎 lamndondira fii fiyaaku maﾉ橡兎 on aduna."
  52,26,"ﾆ‘ jaabora ﾉ兎 wiide : pellet, men laatino aduna, ko men hulunooﾉ兎 lepte Allah ﾉ容n, hakkunde yimﾉ兎 amen ﾉ兎n."
  52,27,"Allah moﾆｴﾆｴorii e amen, feewugol e lislaamu, O daﾉ預ndi men lepte norngal Yiite."
  52,28,"Men laatino e nguurndam amen aduna, meﾉ容n rewaynoo Mo men toroo Mo daﾉ溶dugol men Yiite. Tawde pellet, ko Kanko woni moﾆｴﾆｴo goonguﾉ熔 e ko O fodi jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n kon, Hinnotooﾉ熔 ﾉ兎. Hino jeyaa e ko O moﾆｴﾆｴorii e amen O yurmii men : fewnugol men e gomﾉ擁nal, naada men Aljanna, woﾉ遼擁na men e Yiite."
  52,29,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, anndintinir tun Alqur'aanaa, sabu ko neema gomﾉ擁nal e haqqil ko Allah yeﾉ蓉 maaﾉ預 kon, a wonaa ndureejo gollidoowo e jinna, a wonaa kadi feetuﾉ熔."
  52,30,"Kaa ﾉ兎e fennooﾉ兎 wi'au wonnde : Muhammadu wanaa Nulaaﾉ熔, ko yimoowo ! Mo men habbitanii tun biftagol maayde, men pooftoo e makko."
  52,31,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan ﾉ兎 : awa habbitee maayde am ! Min kadi miﾉ熔 habbitii nde lepte ﾉ容n yanata e mon, sabu ko fennuﾉ熔 lam kon."